Word Graphs

  Useful for NPC conversations and "that reminds me of..."


Words

    Must distinguish between "wood" as noun, "wood" as adjective, "stone"
      as noun, adj, verb, etc.

  Noun
      Must point to Plural, Possessive forms (poss. for details)

  Verb
      Later on, need many tenses/forms.  Early on, second-person command
        form is fine.

  Adjective

  Adverb
      Useful with verbs, esp. social verbs

  Article
      Definite, indefinite -- gendered for some languages

